						               													<description>Battle Arena Show is a board game that incorporates strategy and action of the MOBA (Multiplayer Online Battle Arena) video games. Two to six players organize themselves into two opposing teams, each with the goal of destroying the enemy&amp;rsquo;s base in order to win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The key to victory is collaborative team-play and strategic reasoning. Each team is composed of three champions and twelve minions, represented by highly-detailed miniatures.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Battle Arena Show takes place in an alternative reality, where the discovery of time travel allows for unprecedented technological advances. In a world devastated by warfare, a morbid television program broadcasts battles to entertain the masses. There are champions from all over the world and from every imaginable era in each opposing team, but all must strive to destroy the enemy base in order to earn the coveted title of Battle Arena Master.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
